				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\delta$$\end{document}, may differ between different sheets of synthetic rubber, applied as antenna substrate. Consequently, small variations in ϵr\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
